kratos-clone
============

This project is a fork of and extends asimov-academy/Website-Downloader:
  https://github.com/asimov-academy/Website-Downloader

The original Website-Downloader is authored by Asimov Academy and was
published with the following note in its README:

  "Uso pessoal e educacional."  (Personal and educational use.)

The original author did not publish an explicit OSI-approved license file,
so the original sources retain their original terms. This fork's MIT license
applies only to original contributions made in this repository, including:

  - kratos_clone/ (hardened Playwright capture module)
  - scripts/ (design system inventory + generators)
  - docs/ (PROMPT_v2, WORKFLOW, PERSONALIZATION specs)
  - LICENSE, NOTICE, CI configuration files

Modifications to upstream files (e.g., downloader.py) carry the same
"personal and educational use" terms as the original work.

For commercial use of any code derived from the upstream Website-Downloader,
contact Asimov Academy directly.
